# Summary

I really want to make a project with an e-ink display.
This project is part 1 of that project.

Weatherboy takes a weather forecast for a zipcode and asks ChatGPT to describe it in an image involving a cute animal.
The cute animal is randomly chosen from a very large text file instead of asking ChatGPT, because when you ask ChatGPT to choose "randomly" it will end up choosing the same 3-5 things.

I then take the description and send it to Dall-E, along with some randomly chosen artistic style and HD modifier.
